                answer: { zh: "PES = (80/200) / (2/8) = 0.4 / 0.25 = 1.6 (弹性供给)。供给量变化百分比 = 40%，价格变化百分比 = 25%。", en: "PES = (80/200) ÷ (2/8) = 0.4 ÷ 0.25 = 1.6 (elastic supply). % change in quantity = 40%, % change in price = 25%." }
