                answer: { zh: "(a) 均衡: Qd = Qs → 100 - 2P = 20 + 3P → 5P = 80 → P = £16, Q = 100 - 2(16) = 68 (b) 价格上限£12 < 均衡价格£16 → 有约束力。Qd = 100 - 2(12) = 76, Qs = 20 + 3(12) = 56 → 短缺 = 76 - 56 = 20 单位。会出现排队、黑市、配给制。", en: "(a) Equilibrium: Qd = Qs → 100 - 2P = 20 + 3P → 5P = 80 → P = £16, Q = 68 (b) Price ceiling £12 < equilibrium £16 → binding. Qd = 76, Qs = 56 → shortage = 20 units. Results in queuing, black markets, rationing." }
