                answer: { zh: "(a) 价格下限£8 > 均衡价格£6 → 有约束力。在£8价格下，Qs > Qd → 产生剩余（过剩供给）。农民生产过多，消费者购买过少。(b) 政府选项: ①购买剩余产品并储存（如欧盟黄油山）②提供补贴鼓励出口 ③限制生产配额 ④销毁剩余产品。所有选项都有成本。", en: "(a) Price floor £8 > equilibrium £6 → binding. At £8, Qs > Qd → surplus. Farmers produce too much, consumers buy too little. (b) Government options: ①Buy surplus and store (EU butter mountains) ②Subsidise exports ③Production quotas ④Destroy surplus. All options costly." }
