                answer: { zh: "(a) 名义增长率 = (2200-2000)/2000 × 100% = 10% (b) 2022实际GDP = 2000/100×100 = £2000bn; 2023实际GDP = 2200/105×100 = £2095bn; 实际增长率 = (2095-2000)/2000 × 100% = 4.75% (c) 差异(10% - 4.75% = 5.25%)是通货膨胀造成的。名义增长包含价格上涨，实际增长剔除了通胀影响，反映真实产出增长。", en: "(a) Nominal growth = 10% (b) 2022 real GDP = £2000bn; 2023 real GDP = £2095bn; Real growth = 4.75% (c) Difference (5.25%) is due to inflation. Nominal growth includes price increases, real growth removes inflation effect and shows true output growth." }
