                answer: { zh: "(a) 劳动力 = 就业 + 失业 = 1600万 + 100万 = 1700万 (b) 失业率 = 100/1700 × 100% = 5.88% (c) 劳动力参与率 = 1700/2000 × 100% = 85%。注意:非劳动力(300万)不计入失业，因为他们没有积极寻找工作。", en: "(a) Labor force = 16m + 1m = 17m (b) Unemployment rate = 1/17 × 100% = 5.88% (c) LFPR = 17/20 × 100% = 85%. Note: Not in labor force (3m) not counted as unemployed because they're not actively seeking work." }
