                question: { zh: "CPI从120上升到126。(a) 计算通货膨胀率 (b) 如果名义工资增长3%，实际工资如何变化？(c) 如果名义利率为7%，实际利率是多少？", en: "CPI rises from 120 to 126. (a) Calculate inflation rate (b) If nominal wage rises 3%, what happens to real wage? (c) If nominal interest rate is 7%, what is real interest rate?" },
                answer: { zh: "(a) 通胀率 = (126-120)/120 × 100% = 5% (b) 实际工资变化 = 名义工资增长 - 通胀率 = 3% - 5% = -2%。实际工资下降2%，购买力减弱。(c) 实际利率 = 名义利率 - 通胀率 = 7% - 5% = 2%。储蓄者实际获得2%的回报。", en: "(a) Inflation = 5% (b) Real wage change = 3% - 5% = -2%. Real wage falls 2%, purchasing power declines. (c) Real interest rate = 7% - 5% = 2%. Savers earn real return of 2%." }
