                answer: { zh: "(a) 自主消费a=50(收入为0时的消费，通过借贷或动用储蓄)；MPC=0.75(每增加£1收入，消费增加£0.75) (b) C = 50 + 0.75(200) = 50 + 150 = 200; S = Y - C = 200 - 200 = 0 (c) 储蓄函数: S = -a + (1-b)Y = -50 + 0.25Y。当Y=200时，S = -50 + 0.25(200) = 0 ✓", en: "(a) Autonomous consumption a=50 (consumption at zero income, financed by borrowing/dissaving); MPC=0.75 (each £1 income increase → £0.75 consumption increase) (b) C=200; S=0 (c) Savings function: S = -50 + 0.25Y. When Y=200, S=0 ✓" }
