              "BIOLOGICAL THEORIES STRENGTHS - Scientific evidence with brain scans and biochemical measures",

              "BIOLOGICAL THEORIES LIMITATIONS - Reductionist ignores social factors and correlation not causation",

              "FREUD'S PERSONALITY STRUCTURE - Id ego and superego determine moral behavior",

              "WEAK SUPEREGO - Inadequate moral development leads to lack of guilt and conscience",

              "OVERACTIVE SUPEREGO - Excessive guilt leads to unconscious desire for punishment through crime",

              "BOWLBY'S MATERNAL DEPRIVATION - Early separation leads to affectionless psychopathy",

              "AFFECTIONLESS PSYCHOPATHY - Lack of empathy guilt and emotional connection to others",

              "PSYCHODYNAMIC THEORIES STRENGTHS - Emphasizes early childhood experiences and attachment",

