              "EYSENCK'S THEORY STRENGTHS - Scientific with measurable questionnaire and research support",

              "EYSENCK'S THEORY LIMITATIONS - Self-report bias and cultural bias in personality dimensions",

              "COGNITIVE BEHAVIORAL THERAPY - Changes thinking patterns and behaviors leading to crime",

